{"tid":1722643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首爾市立大學有連儂牆支持香港","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:15:30.000Z","uid":168020,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0472b2a14c8b0255f32db5feb314b0b426b72461","tid":1722643,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"韓國大學生/市民真係好支持今似既抗爭<br />\n<br />\n幾 首爾大 高麗大之後 首爾市立大（清涼里個間）<br />\n<br />\n又多一間大學出現連儂牆 啲打氣既字條貼滿晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就連學校保安哥哥 同清潔既姐姐們都留言支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢啲起唔到咩大作用 但至少同香港手足講 <br />\n<br />\n你地一啲都唔孤單 <br />\n<br />\n真心覺得we connect 埋韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以我所知 咁多位留韓既香港人都好努力同自己間U<br />\n申請緊貼大字報同整連儂牆 在韓手足都要加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCNQyVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCNQyVj.png&h=2532c6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNLFV8G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNLFV8G.png&h=42130a00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeAR2OJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeAR2OJ.png&h=6de5eb43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hzSNfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hzSNfq.png&h=99828282&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bb23348e11df5f7f2382958d5545fe202d66c14","tid":1722643,"uid":168020,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"最後 如果係韓國既咁多位<br />\nG20團隊搞左個圖片展喺弘大 <br />\n今日起去到星期日<br />\n有時間一齊去支持下佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">時間：今日起 - 星期日 12:00-20:00<br />\n地點：마포구 양화로16길 14-16(서교동)위안빌딩 지하1픙<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fyqOkCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfyqOkCD.jpg&h=85502acb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"360884327570f86537ebc7ad51f7750daedd94f6","tid":1722643,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:06:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>【黑警陷入恐慌!】微博瘋傳13休班警被伏擊</strong><br />\n對家士氣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> -40</strong></span></span><br />\n何必再送頭？<br />\n始終踢春袋先係最本少利大，<br />\n我地需要極大量呢類型行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1722529/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1722529/</a>"},{"pid":"fc82315279b76f4a02001c2a35596964d03c0890","tid":1722643,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:09:17.000Z","msg":"thank you koreans"},{"pid":"a29b80e09f14dd70eacb7ad37f1d2b7358251ec4","tid":1722643,"uid":297981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"人地幫唔係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝曬"},{"pid":"fee2558d978ce5218724201fb51a99132df1fc97","tid":1722643,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a29b80e09f14dd70eacb7ad37f1d2b7358251ec4","tid":1722643,"uid":297981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"人地幫唔係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要多謝韓國啊 嚟多啲韓國玩啦"},{"pid":"102129089b1dabc6c158e78ab7b1d8404e43ca99","tid":1722643,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"小粉紅又會頂唔順去破壞啦"},{"pid":"83046326762371d8c1b90b4b22670d3604571387","tid":1722643,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"37eb891aef88ff1e72